Perry Drug Stores Inc saidFebruary sales were up 19.5 pct to 52 mln dlrs from 43 mln dlrsa year earlier, with same-store sales up five pct.    It said sales for the first four months of its fiscal yearwere up 17.0 pct to 241 mln dlrs from 206 mln dlrs a yearbefore, with same-store sales up five pct. Reuter&#3;